To provide you with easy access to experience, sometimes we will be on your computer or place small data files on the mobile device to recognize your identity, these data files may be Cookie,Flash Cookie, or your browser or application associated with other local store (collectively, "Cookie"). Cookie is a text file, stored on your computer by the site server or on a mobile device, and only the server can retrieve or read the contents of the Cookie. For browsers, each Cookie is unique. He includes some anonymous information, such as the unique identifier, the website name and some numbers and numbers. He can allow websites to remember your preferences or your shopping cart contents, and so on.
 　　Most large Web sites or Internet service provider for your visit (using the [session-Cookie]) or visit (use [sustainability Cookie]), enabling the site [remember] your function in order to improve the user experience. Cookie can help the site remember your setting, when browsing the site on your computer or mobile device using language, font size and other preferences each time you return to Web sites, you do not need to enter the settings again. If a Web site does not use the Cookie whenever you when moved to a new Web page on the site, you will be treated as a new visitor, for example, when you enter data in detail, and move to another page, the page will not be able to identify your identity, also could not keep you logged in.
 　　Our Cookie will not be used for is your personal identity is used only when you access the Web site to work better and more convenient. If needed, you can delete all the Cookie on your computer, you can also use your browser settings to disable Cookie. However, if you delete or disable Cookie, each time you visit our Web site, you may have to manually adjust some preferences.
 　　Our Cookie will not be used for any purpose other than those mentioned in the text, also not used to collect any personal data for any other purpose.
